1-4: Coleman Hawkins (ts), Benny Carter (tp, cl, as), George Chisholm (tb), Jimmy Williams (cl, as), Freddie Johnson (p), Ray Webb (g), Len Harrison (b), Robert Montmarche (d); The Hague, 1937

1994 Fourstar "Masters Of Jazz"

This CD sounds better than the Affinity box set (the cd version, I haven't heard the vinyl, if it exists, I know the Django box set was issued on vinyl, I haven't heard that either. Anyway, if I could get the CH and DR box sets with the same sound quality as this CD, I would be more or less content.) on which all these tracks are also present
